#

Tofu Curry

30 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

SoyCoconut

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Indian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickComfort FoodVegan Option

Description

A creamy and flavorful curry packed with protein-rich tofu and vibrant spices, perfect for a quick weeknight dinner.

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 14 oz
  • coconut milk: 1 can (13.5 oz)
  • curry powder: 2 tablespoons
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • ginger: 1 tablespoon, minced
  • bell pepper: 1, chopped
  • spinach: 2 cups, fresh
  • salt: to taste
  • cooked rice: for serving
